'''DYXX-TV''' is a commercial translator television station owned by [[Intercontinental Broadcasting Corporation]]. It's studio and transmitter are located at Barangay Lawa-an, [[Roxas City]], [[Philippines]]. This station is now inactive due to weather conditions.
